{"id":232417751,"title":"分享啤酒瑜珈活動","content":"https://i.imgur.com/LkBydjm.jpg\n啤酒+瑜珈可不單單只是噱頭\n也不只是因為好玩（當然它非常好玩）\n啤酒瑜珈首次開課在德國柏林\n由瑜珈老師Jhula發明\n而將啤酒與瑜珈結合的理由則是：\n「我們發現瑜珈可以和喝啤酒後的愉悅感相互結合，進而達到意識中更高的心靈層次。」\n\n既然都要運動了，為啥還要喝高熱量的啤酒？\n這可不是為了單純增加樂趣，而去喝啤酒運動的！\nhttps://i.imgur.com/GchFXSA.jpg\n然而，喝啤酒做瑜珈能活化副交感神經，對於放鬆肌肉和加速血液循環都有幫助，練習瑜珈的過程中飲用啤酒讓體溫能更快上升、增加代謝、加速流汗量，大大提升了運動的效果。\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/AxUMcfI.jpg\n說了這麼多，你對啤酒瑜珈有興趣嗎？\n除了瑜珈在週末好好放鬆\n還有小遊戲可以獲得超值獎品\n\n12/27星期五 \n晚上8：00～9：30\n金蘋果樹舞蹈工作室\n活動連結：https://www.accupass.com/go/lexie_beeryoga\n\n\n*如有違反，請告知改善，謝謝🙏","excerpt":"啤酒+瑜珈可不單單只是噱頭，也不只是因為好玩（當然它非常好玩），啤酒瑜珈首次開課在德國柏林，由瑜珈老師Jhula發明，而將啤酒與瑜珈結合的理由則是：「我們發現瑜珈可以和喝啤酒後的愉悅感相互結合，進而達","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"2bb20844-07ec-41d3-830f-ae551fc31246","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-01T11:41:21.027Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-01T11:42:23.445Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["課程","瑜珈","啤酒","運動","大學"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"課程","forumAlias":"course","school":"萊西Lexie","department":"lexieslive24","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/LkBydjm.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/GchFXSA.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/AxUMcfI.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"cff8c323-e7db-4f57-a968-e1c4aed9e768","url":"https://i.imgur.com/LkBydjml.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/LkBydjml.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/LkBydjml.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-01T11:41:21.027Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-01T11:42:23.445Z"},{"id":"cff8c323-e7db-4f57-a968-e1c4aed9e768","url":"https://i.imgur.com/LkBydjm.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/L